<h1 id='minimize'>Minimize</h1>
<p>Clicking the Minimize link sends the wallet to the task bar notification area 
(aka system tray).</p>

<p><img src="/images/img/minimze-to-task-bar-notification-ar%0Aea.png" alt="minimze-to-task-bar-notification-area" /></p>

<p>Click the XAYA icon in the task bar notification area, or right-click it and 
choose &quot;Show App&quot;.</p>

<p><img src="/images/img/minimize-show-app.png" alt="minimize-show-app" /></p>

<p>You can also shut down the XAYA Electron wallet and XAYA daemon by clicking 
&quot;Quit&quot;.</p>
